### Travel Planner API Test File
### Use this to test the conversational agent without the frontend

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071/api

# =============================================================================
# 1. Create a new conversation with ALL trip details upfront
# =============================================================================
# This provides everything the agent needs to call PlanTrip immediately

### Start planning with complete details
# @name createConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/create
Content-Type: text/plain
Accept: text/plain

Hi! I'm John Smith and I'd like to plan a trip. Here are all my details:
- Preferences: beach and relaxation with some cultural experiences
- Duration: 7 days
- Budget: $5000 USD
- Travel dates: March 15-22, 2026
- Special requirements: vegetarian meals preferred

Please start planning my trip!

###

# =============================================================================
# 2. Follow-up messages (use conversationId from previous response)
# =============================================================================

@conversationId = <paste-conversation-id-here>

### Check on progress
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat/{{conversationId}}
Content-Type: text/plain
Accept: text/plain

How is my trip planning going?

###

### Ask about the plan details
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat/{{conversationId}}
Content-Type: text/plain
Accept: text/plain

What restaurants did you recommend?

###

### Ask about itinerary
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat/{{conversationId}}
Content-Type: text/plain
Accept: text/plain

What are we doing on day 2?

###

### Approve the trip
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat/{{conversationId}}
Content-Type: text/plain
Accept: text/plain

Yes, please approve and book this trip!

###

### Reject the trip
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat/{{conversationId}}
Content-Type: text/plain
Accept: text/plain

Actually, I'd like to reject this plan. The budget is too high.

###

# =============================================================================
# 3. Alternative: Adventure trip request
# =============================================================================

### Adventure trip
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/create
Content-Type: text/plain
Accept: text/plain

I'm Sarah Johnson looking for an adventure trip.
- Type: adventure and hiking
- Duration: 5 days
- Budget: $3000 USD
- Dates: April 1-5, 2026
- Requirements: I need wheelchair accessible accommodations

Start planning!

###

# =============================================================================
# 4. Direct orchestration status (if you have the orchestration ID)
# =============================================================================

@orchestrationId = <paste-orchestration-id-here>

### Get orchestration status directly
GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/orchestration/{{orchestrationId}}

###

### Approve orchestration directly (bypassing the agent)
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/orchestration/{{orchestrationId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "approved": true,
    "comments": "Looks great, book it!"
}

###

### Reject orchestration directly
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/orchestration/{{orchestrationId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "approved": false,
    "comments": "Too expensive, please find cheaper options"
}
